    "updated_at": "2024-08-21T18:02:57Z",
    "body": "I had a similar issue which I think was related to the terminal type used in `tmux`. I had to set:\r\n\r\n```\r\n# Default is \"tmux-256color\"\r\nset-option -g default-terminal \"screen-256color\"\r\n```\r\n\r\nMight be useful to someone else, or help get to the bottom of the underlying cause...\r\n\r\n",
    "author_association": "NONE",
